Not in any order

* Tooltips containing the notes from the Packaging Policy for each widget
* Modularize creation of widgets and their layouts
* Replace wx.TextCtrl for required items to be wx.PyValidators that are checked
  during package submission. This way we can notify the user with visual aids
  that such fields are improperly formatted. We can use this to verify that a
  value exists, that it does not contain improper characters, and that it fits
  a the proper structure (ie. email address verified by regex)